import { Box, Container, Paper, Grid, TextField, IconButton, Button } from '@mui/material'
import React, { useState } from 'react'
import DeleteOutlineIcon from '@mui/icons-material/DeleteOutline';
function DynamicForm() {
    const userTemplates = {name:"", email:"", phone:"", address:""};
    const [user, setUser] = useState([userTemplates])
  return (
    <Container>
    <Paper component={Box} p={4} mx="auto">
    {user.map((user, index)=>(
    
        <Grid container  spacing={3} key={index}>
        <Grid item md={3} sx={{marginBottom:""}}>
           <TextField  
            label="Name"
            placeholder="Enter your full name"
            variant='outlined'
            fullWidth
           />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item md={3} sx={{marginBottom:""}}>
           <TextField  
            label="Email"
            placeholder="Enter your Email address"
            variant='outlined'
            fullWidth
           />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item md={2} sx={{marginBottom:""}}>
           <TextField  
            label="Phone"
            placeholder="Enter your phone number"
            variant='outlined'
            fullWidth
           />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item md={3} sx={{marginBottom:""}}>
           <TextField  
            label="Address"
            placeholder="Enter your full address"
            variant='outlined'
            fullWidth
           />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item md={1}sx={{marginBottom:""}}>
        <IconButton color="secondary">
            <DeleteOutlineIcon/>
        </IconButton>
          
        </Grid>
    </Grid>
    ))}
   <Button variant='contained' color="primary">Add More</Button>
    </Paper>
       </Container>

  )
}

export default DynamicForm
